WARNING: kexec works just like 'reboot', so please save your data before using it!

Loading the new kernel:

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# kexec -l /boot/vmlinuz-2.6.18-fw1 --append="ro root=/dev/hda3 quiet vga=792 resume=/dev/hda2"
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Booting it:

----------
# kexec -e
----------
